      <chapter id="646">
        <pagenum>2</pagenum>
        <subchapter>0</subchapter>
        <title>Basic skills</title>
        <content>&lt;h1 class="Subhead"&gt;Basic Skills&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h1 class="Subhead"&gt;&lt;i style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.231;"&gt;Basic skills&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.231;"&gt; refer to the kinds of academic skills we learn in school.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Topics such as:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;English language (spoken);&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;reading comprehension (English);&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="line-height: 1.231;"&gt;written English;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b style="line-height: 1.231;"&gt;mathematics;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="line-height: 1.231;"&gt;science;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="line-height: 1.231;"&gt;government/economics;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="line-height: 1.231;"&gt;humanities/arts;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="line-height: 1.231;"&gt;foreign languages; and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="line-height: 1.231;"&gt;history/geography.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note that skills listed in bold were reported by employers as most critical. Let’s take a closer look at these particular basic skills.&lt;/p&gt;</content>
