      <chapter id="648">
        <pagenum>4</pagenum>
        <subchapter>0</subchapter>
        <title>Basic math skills</title>
        <content>&lt;h1 class="Subhead"&gt;Basic math skills&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Basic Math&lt;/i&gt; – This is the ability to perform pre-algebra math and to apply basic math concepts to everyday problems. Often we refer to this level as arithmetic or “functional math.”  Most jobs require this level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/134187843.jpg" width="600" height="399" alt="Photo of a woman creating a graph on a whiteboard." /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
