      <chapter id="650">
        <pagenum>6</pagenum>
        <subchapter>0</subchapter>
        <title>Teamwork</title>
        <content>&lt;h1 class="Subhead"&gt;Applied skills – teamwork&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Very few jobs in our society do not depend on some degree of &lt;i&gt;teamwork&lt;/i&gt;, which is defined as the ability to collaborate with one or more people to accomplish identified goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt; &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/138030903.jpg" width="620" height="412" alt="Photo of four hands holding puzzle pieces." /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt; &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class="p1"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
