      <chapter id="651">
        <pagenum>7</pagenum>
        <subchapter>0</subchapter>
        <title>Critical thinking/problem-solving</title>
        <content>&lt;h1 class="Subhead"&gt;Applied skills – critical thinking/problem-solving&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All jobs require &lt;i&gt;critical thinking and problem-solving skills&lt;/i&gt;, which refer to the ability to analyze a multidimensional problem or scenario, to generate possible solutions, to test the possible solutions, and to communicate one’s findings to others.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt; &lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/87460442.jpg" width="540" height="655" alt="Photo of a three people at a computer." style="float: left;" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
