      <chapter id="652">
        <pagenum>8</pagenum>
        <subchapter>0</subchapter>
        <title>Communication</title>
        <content>&lt;h1 class="Subhead"&gt;Applied skills - communication&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Most jobs demand that a worker be able to communicate effectively. &lt;i&gt;Communication skills&lt;/i&gt; refer to the ability to receive and give information in an accurate manner. This can be conveyed in many ways: orally, in writing, or through gestures, codes or assistive communication devices.&lt;/p&gt;</content>
