        <pagenum>9</pagenum>
        <subchapter>0</subchapter>
        <title>Professionalism/work ethic</title>
        <content>&lt;h1 class="Subhead"&gt;Applied skills - professionalism/work ethic&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Professionalism/Work Ethic:&lt;/i&gt;&lt;b&gt; &lt;/b&gt;These skills refer to character and behavior qualities that enable individuals to succeed in work, education and social environments. &lt;/p&gt;</content>
