      <chapter id="654">
        <pagenum>10</pagenum>
        <subchapter>0</subchapter>
        <title>Information technology application</title>
        <content>&lt;h1 class="Subhead"&gt;Applied skills – information technology application&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Information Technology Application&lt;/i&gt;: Most jobs require workers to interact in some way with technology. Even lower skill level jobs increasingly require employees to use computers and/or handheld devices (for example, in some hotels, housekeepers use computers to order supplies and communicate room status).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
