&lt;li&gt;Communication – with other team members, and in presenting to the class.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Critical thinking/problem-solving – in determining how to approach the assignment, determining how to present information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creativity/innovation – in designing a presentation to demonstrate their understanding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;And information technology application – required in order to create an element of the presentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In addition, this assignment directly addressed reading skills, and for some teams, writing skills as well.&lt;/li&gt;
